===phase_5_corruption===
<b>Phase 5</b> # CLASS: w3-green
This symbol indicates a ring should be used where the condition is met and the required die in unavailable # CLASS: w3-green # IMAGE: elvenring3.png
-> shadow_under_threat

===shadow_under_threat===
<b>Shadow under <i>threat</i> or Free People <i>exposed</i></b>? # CLASS: w3-yellow # IMAGE: elvenring3.png
+ [Yes] -> mobile_army_adjacent
+ [No] -> character_cards_over_zero

===mobile_army_adjacent===
<i>Mobile</i> army adjacent to <i>threat</i>? # CLASS: w3-blue
+ [Yes] -> attack_character_die
+ [No] -> move_create_mobile_army

===attack_character_die===
Attack using character die # CLASS: w3-pink  # IMAGE: ADSAcharacter.png
-> attack_army_die

===attack_army_die===
Attack using army die # CLASS: w3-pink  # IMAGE: ADSAarmy.png
-> move_create_mobile_army

===move_create_mobile_army===
Move can create <i>mobile</i> army adjacent to <i>threat</i>? # CLASS: w3-blue
+ [Yes] -> move_character_die
+ [No] -> move_increase_troops

===move_increase_troops===
Move can increase troop numbers in the Stronghold under <i>threat</i>? # CLASS: w3-blue
+ [Yes] -> move_character_die
+ [No] -> mobile_army_route

===mobile_army_route===
<i>Mobile</i> army's route to closest <i>target</i> takes it towards <i>threat</i>? # CLASS: w3-blue
+ [Yes] -> move_character_die
+ [No] -> move_towards_exposed

===move_character_die===
Move using character die # CLASS: w3-pink # IMAGE: ADSAcharacter.png
~ return_knot = -> stronghold_under_threat
-> army

===move_towards_exposed===
Can move towards <i>exposed</i>? # CLASS: w3-blue
+ [Yes] -> move_character_die
+ [No] -> stronghold_under_threat

===stronghold_under_threat===
Stronghold under <i>threat</i> is valid for muster? # CLASS: w3-blue
~ return_knot = -> threat_sieging
+ [Yes] -> muster
+ [No] -> threat_sieging

===threat_sieging===
<i>Threat</i> is sieging a Shadow stronghold which can use more leadership? # CLASS: w3-blue
~ return_knot = -> character_cards_over_zero
+ [Yes] -> character_2
+ [No] -> character_cards_over_zero